; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB54B5FFF92FFC36507FF6858DAFABC" author="Bamou, R. &amp; Mbakop, L. R. &amp; Kopya, E. &amp; Ndo, C. &amp; Awono-Ambene, P. &amp; Tchuinkam, T. &amp; Rono, M. K. &amp; Mwangangi, J. &amp; Nkondjio, C." box="[291,507,1899,1926]" pageId="10" pageNumber="192" pagination="464" refId="ref6986" refString="Bamou, R., Mbakop, L. R., Kopya, E., Ndo, C., Awono-Ambene, P., Tchuinkam, T., Rono, M. K., Mwangangi, J. &amp; Antonio- Nkondjio, C. (2018) Changes in malaria vector bionomics and transmission patterns in the equatorial forest region of Cameroon between 2000 and 2017. Parasites &amp; Vectors, 11, 464. https: // doi. org / 10.1186 / s 13071 - 018 - 3049 - 4" type="journal article" year="2018">
